```plantuml
@startuml xinsongyan_talos_pal_locomotion_slmc

actor Operator

participant "ROS" as ROS
participant "WBC Framework" as WBC
participant "DCM Controller" as DCM
participant "State Estimator" as Estimator
participant "Safety Layer" as Safety
participant "Simulator" as Simulator

Operator -> ROS: Start Locomotion Controller
ROS -> WBC: Load WBC Plugin
WBC -> DCM: Request Walking Pattern

DCM -> WBC: Provide Reference Trajectory
activate WBC
WBC -> Estimator: Get Pose and Velocity
Estimator -> WBC: Provide Estimated State

WBC -> Safety: Check Safety Conditions
Safety -> WBC: Confirm Safe Operation
WBC -> Simulator: Send Control Commands
Simulator -> WBC: Provide Simulation Feedback

WBC -> ROS: Report Status
ROS -> Operator: Display Status

@enduml
```